universe of origin : The desert margins and the embalming hall — Serqet-hetyt, "she who tightens the throat," the scorpion goddess whose very name is the constriction of the windpipe, guardian of the canopic Qebehsenuef and of the bound and narrowed breath
seal               : The open channel is a blessing precisely because the scorpion can tighten the throat to a thread.
